# Teaching: WAI Closeout v2 — Adoption Marker Sync + Hub Signal Bulletin

**Type:** Protocol Enhancement
**Version:** 2.0.0
**Created:** 2026-03-22
**Safe to Auto-Adopt:** true
**Affects:** Closeout protocol, WAI-State.json adoption markers, hub signal distribution
**Supersedes:** wai-closeout-step9b-sender-v1.md.teaching (additive, not replacing)

