## Prerequisites

None — this teaching is standalone and has no dependencies.

## Batch Sequence

**Batch:** canonical-evolution-v2
**Apply order:** 5 of 6
**Depends on:** none
**Required before:** skill-wai-wakeup-hub-bulletin-v1 (T-06) — T-06 relies on hub bulletin dirs this teaching creates
